          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "About Arccos",
            "heading_size": "title-md",
            "heading_tag": "h1",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "text_4RaNeC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Golf’s #1 game tracking platform, Arccos is the Official Game Tracker of the PGA TOUR. A pioneer of connected golf products, Arccos’ mission is to transform the golfing experience by seamlessly combining automatic shot tracking with Artificial Intelligence and Stroke Gained analytics. By allowing golfers to track their game like the pros and delivering powerful, personalized insights, Arccos helps them play smarter and shoot lower scores.</p><p>Among Arccos’ investors are many of golf’s biggest brands and most impactful businesses, including the <strong>PGA TOUR, PING, Inc., TaylorMade Golf Company, Cobra PUMA Golf, Topgolf Callaway Brands Corp. (NYSE: MODG), </strong>and others.</p><p>Arccos also partners with <strong>Srixon-Cleveland Golf, CBS Sports, ESPN/PGA TOUR Live, Golf Channel, Club Champion, EA Sports, Golf Digest, Golf Monthly, Me and My Golf, The Stack System </strong>and <strong>Skillest</strong>.</p><p>Listed among the “World’s Most Innovative Companies” by Fast Company, Arccos boasts the golf industry’s richest data set. This includes 1.2 billion shots taken during more than 22 million rounds played by Arccos members on courses in 160 countries.</p><p>Named after the inverse function of cosine – an element of advanced mathematics that is featured in the Arccos algorithm – Arccos has received awards from media and business organizations worldwide, including Forbes, Entrepreneur Magazine, Golf Digest, GOLF Magazine, Golf Channel, MyGolfSpy, National Golf Foundation, Golf Monthly, Golf Today, SCOREGolf, Connecticut Technology Council, ING, Gear Patrol and the PGA of America, among others.</p>",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "text_font": "body",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
