        },
        "text_xR6CEq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Sal Syed, the CEO of Arccos Golf, embarked on a journey to create an innovative product fueled by his passion for both golf and technology.</p><p>During his pursuit of an MBA at the Yale University School of Management, Sal crossed paths with co-founder Clinton Grusd. Together, they laid the foundation for the business, developing crucial concepts, plans, and strategies that now drive Arccos.</p><p>Joining forces with his childhood friend, Ammad Faisal, the trio recognized the absence of a high-performing, comprehensive tool in the golfing world to effectively track and analyze a golfer's game, ultimately enhancing decision-making on the course. Driven by this realization, they set out to revolutionize the way golf is approached and played.</p><p>Through the collaboration of brilliant minds, including PhDs, engineers, designers, and PGA Professionals, they successfully launched a groundbreaking product that is making waves in the golfing community: Arccos.</p>",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "text_font": "body",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
